      "description": "Affordable and straightforward, this vehicle offers a practical opportunity for someone in need of low-cost transportation or a project with potential. It shows its age and wear, but delivers strong value at an accessible price point. If you\u2019re looking for an inexpensive way to get on the road without overcommitting, this is a smart option worth a closer look.",
