      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable project, runabout, or handy parts donor? This car is being sold in poor condition, but it still has plenty to offer for the right buyer. A great budget-friendly option for someone who enjoys tinkering, needs something inexpensive to work with, or wants a practical base for a project. Priced to reflect its condition and make for a straightforward, honest sale.",
