    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid project car with good bones and the kind of mechanical simplicity enthusiasts appreciate. Engine starts, runs, and delivers usable power, transmission engages as it should, and the chassis feels fundamentally honest. Not a showpiece, but a capable driver/project with strong parts value, straightforward serviceability, and plenty of upside for someone who knows their way around a toolbox. Great candidate for a budget build, weekend runabout, or dependable backup with some cosmetic and finishing needs.",
      "price": 7900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
