      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Built with the kind of honest character you can\u2019t fake, this car has a seasoned presence and a story in every mile. It\u2019s the sort of ride that feels right at home as a dependable around-town companion, a practical project, or an affordable set of wheels with plenty of life left to give in the hands of its next owner. If you appreciate substance, simplicity, and the chance to make something your own, this one offers a compelling starting point at a budget-friendly price.",
      "price": 5900.0,
